OL,3,CMore than 1,700 Brits taking legal
OL,4,Caction over Tui Cape Verde illnesses
OL,6,FA total of eight Brits have died after
OL,7,Ffalling sick on Tui holidays in the
OL,8,FCape Verde, with more than 1,700 now
OL,9,Finvolved in legal action against the
OL,10,Ftravel agency, lawyers have said.
OL,12,FHundreds of people were revealed to be
OL,13,Fsuing Tui in 2023 after being struck
OL,14,Fby stomach bugs on the islands close
OL,15,Fto West Africa, but the number of
OL,16,Fclaimants has only grown since then.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
