OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1775635511
OL,3,CMore than 1,700 Brits taking legal
OL,4,Caction over Tui Cape Verde illnesses
OL,6,FLaw firm Irwin Mitchell has now said
OL,7,Fthey are representing 1,700 UK
OL,8,Ftourists, including the families of
OL,9,Feight Brits who died in connection
OL,10,Fwith their illness since January 2023.
OL,12,F"We continue to be contacted by
OL,13,Fhundreds more people reporting all too
OL,14,Ffamiliar and worrying first-hand
OL,15,Faccounts of how their holidays have
OL,16,Fbeen ruined by serious illness,"
OL,17,FJatinder Paul, international serious
OL,18,Finjury lawyer at Irwin Mitchell, told
OL,19,FITV News.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
