PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1775635511
OL,3,CMore than 1,700 Brits taking legal
OL,4,Caction over Tui Cape Verde illnesses
OL,6,F"Our focus remains on establishing the
OL,7,Ffull facts of how these holidaymakers
OL,8,Ffell ill, but this latest development
OL,9,Fis of great concern."
OL,11,FUK health officials issued a warning
OL,12,Fagainst travelling to Cape Verde
OL,13,Fearlier this year.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
