OL,3,CMore than 1,700 Brits taking legal
OL,4,Caction over Tui Cape Verde illnesses
OL,6,FA spokesperson for TUI UK & I told ITV
OL,7,FNews: "We are deeply saddened by the
OL,8,Freports of these tragic losses and
OL,9,Fextend our sincere condolences to the
OL,10,Ffamilies affected.
OL,12,F"While we cannot comment on individual
OL,13,Fcases, customer health and safety is
OL,14,Falways our highest priority.
OL,16,F"We have established procedures in
OL,17,Fplace to support any customer who
OL,18,Fbecomes unwell while on holiday,
OL,19,Fincluding access to appropriate
OL,20,Fmedical care and assistance in resort.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1775635511
OL,3,CMore than 1,700 Brits taking legal
OL,4,Caction over Tui Cape Verde illnesses
OL,6,F"To provide that support, it is
OL,7,Fimportant that illness is reported to
OL,8,Four teams while customers are in
OL,9,Fdestination. Where this does not
OL,10,Fhappen, it limits the assistance we
OL,11,Fare able to offer at the time.
OL,13,F"We continue to follow FCDO advice and
OL,14,Fengage with hotel partners and
OL,15,Frelevant authorities where
OL,16,Fappropriate."
OL,18,FNot all of the eight Brits have been
OL,19,Fnamed, Irwin Mitchell said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
