OL,3,CMore than 1,700 Brits taking legal
OL,4,Caction over Tui Cape Verde illnesses
OL,6,FElena Walsh, 64, from Birmingham, Mark
OL,7,FAshley, 55, of Bedfordshire, and Karen
OL,8,FPooley, 64 from Gloucester, all died
OL,9,Fin 2025 after contracting severe
OL,10,Fgastric illnesses in Cape Verde.
OL,12,FTwo unnamed men in their 50s, one of
OL,13,Fwhom was a retired firefighter from
OL,14,FCounty Durham, also died in 2025.
OL,16,FJane Pressley, 62, of Gainsborough,
OL,17,Fdied in January 2023 and an unnamed
OL,18,Fman in his 60s from Watford died in
OL,19,FNovember 2024.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1775635511
OL,3,CMore than 1,700 Brits taking legal
OL,4,Caction over Tui Cape Verde illnesses
OL,6,FAnother woman, a retired civil servant
OL,7,Fand mum, 71, from Berkshire died in
OL,8,F2024 from a heart attack on her way
OL,9,Fback to Gatwick from the islands.
OL,11,FShe died around 90 minutes before the
OL,12,Fplane landed, the law firm said.
OL,14,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,15,Fsaid in February it was investigating
OL,16,Fshigella cases linked to travel to the
OL,17,Fisland.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1775635511
OL,3,CMore than 1,700 Brits taking legal
OL,4,Caction over Tui Cape Verde illnesses
OL,6,F"Those affected by illness shouldn't
OL,7,Ffeel pressured into accepting early
OL,8,Fsettlement offer from tour operators
OL,9,Fwithout understanding their full legal
OL,10,Frights. We strongly advise seeking
OL,11,Findependent legal advice," Paul said.
OL,13,F"The effects of gastric illness should
OL,14,Fnever be downplayed as symptoms can
OL,15,Flead to life-long and debilitating
OL,16,Fcomplications and even death."
OL,26,@uD@AOUxD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
